text: Kazyrovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 105 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Ufa, 3 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Kazyrovo
